  "detailed_description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> ALTF4? </strong></h2>The Way You Play Games Is Simple!!<br>Become a somewhat clumsy Knight and overcome Trap!!<br>But the way to get there won't be simple.<br>Will you be able to overcome the various traps and irritating terrains in your way?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Test your reflexes!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > There is no SAVE in this game!!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > It's full of exciting background music and annoying traps!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Don't you feel like you can play better next time every time your character dies?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The various traps will keep driving you to death!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Imagine how good it will feel to overcome those traps and finally clear the game!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Once you get your first clear, why don't you aim for clearing the game at one go?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also play together with Remote Play Together.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> ALTF4? </strong></h2>The Way You Play Games Is Simple!!<br>Become a somewhat clumsy Knight and overcome Trap!!<br>But the way to get there won't be simple.<br>Will you be able to overcome the various traps and irritating terrains in your way?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Test your reflexes!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > There is no SAVE in this game!!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > It's full of exciting background music and annoying traps!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Don't you feel like you can play better next time every time your character dies?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The various traps will keep driving you to death!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Imagine how good it will feel to overcome those traps and finally clear the game!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Once you get your first clear, why don't you aim for clearing the game at one go?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also play together with Remote Play Together.</p></li></ul>",
